## SAMSUNG
## S95C - OLED 4K Smart TV (2023)
## Experience the Wow difference of Samsung OLED

page_content.image_description: The image shows a flat-screen television with a vibrant green background featuring a wave pattern. The television is rectangular in shape and has a black border around it. It displays the words "OED" written in white letters at the bottom of the screen.

page_content:
55', 65', 77'
## Top Features
Samsung OLED Technology
With over 8 million specially engineered self-illuminating pixels, contrast is breathtaking. At its best in-viewing settings with controlled lighting, colour and brightness is stunning and life-like with Samsung's QD-OLED pixels powered by Quantum Dot technology.  1
Infinity One Design
At just 10.6mm in depth, this OLED knows how to draw your eye straight to the action. Its sleek and slim profile is the perfect complement to any room, and delivers a streamlined entertainment setup.
True Dolby Atmos
Lose yourself in the breathtaking realism of cinematic sound, right in your own home. Your Samsung TV features inbuilt up firing speakers and True Dolby Atmos support to deliver larger-than-life audio experiences.  2
Attachable Slim One Connect
Remove clutter with one single 2.5 metre cable that transmits both power and data to your TV from a single Slim One Connect Box.  3
1 Picture quality may vary depending on quality and resolution of source content and viewing conditions.
2 Source content must be Dolby Atmos® enabled for Dolby Atmos® playback. Samsung define 'True Dolby Atmos' as featuring an upwards-firing directional speaker for three dimensional sound. Wireless Dolby Atmos compatible only for selected Samsung soundbars.
3 One cable connects to the One Connect Box which integrates external device cables.
